name: Gucha’chi | Iguana
description: Drawing in ink and paper by José Ángel Santiago, 2021 || There are many words to designate a homosexual in Juchitán, not only "muxe"; they are also called "gucha’chi gueela" which means "green iguana", maybe because they go from stick to stick while climbing trees. ~ Zapotec writer and linguist Víctor Cata. || This is a free edition minted as part of the #OBJKT4OBJKT event || https://www.instagram.com/joseangelsantiago/
